{"tid":2330424,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"喪妻後竟未獲安排入住武肺檢疫中心 謝鋮浚在家自我隔離苦候 立法會議員斥不可接受：分分鐘一條命","createTime":"2020-12-18T04:26:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T06:49:53.000Z","uid":5195,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"3740fa57438008d63e7333bc34bf7c6ddb6355db","tid":2330424,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T04:26:00.000Z","msg":"盲撐梁振英的正義聯盟創辦人李偲嫣前日(本月16日)在家中因嚴重不適送院，送院後不治，當局證實她初步確診武漢肺炎，終年56歲。令人費解的是，作為李偲嫣密切接觸者的丈夫謝鋮浚由前日到昨日，據報竟然要一直留在八鄉元崗新村的寓所內自我隔離，當局既未有讓他入院檢查，亦沒有安排他入住檢疫中心，這對謝先生甚至是鄰居其實都有風險。有立法會議員聲稱謝先生已輪候入住檢疫中心近兩天，卻一直「無人理會」，估計現時有數百名市民如謝先生一樣正苦候入住檢疫中心作檢疫。議員指情況不可接受，因「分分鐘都一條命」，促政府立即跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201218/BIWUNCXEGFHENANRHTBPM3HILU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201218%2FBIWUNCXEGFHENANRHTBPM3HILU%2F&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrahYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=0872b254\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201218%2FBIWUNCXEGFHENANRHTBPM3HILU%2F&h=2c3e36c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201218/BIWUNCXEGFHENANRHTBPM3HILU/</a>"},{"pid":"32cc60782805e2202f6bdedea00d36691eeba4f5","tid":2330424,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T04:26:43.000Z","msg":"哭撚左"},{"pid":"9738e758176cf83700583441e12a710e5c918d5e","tid":2330424,"uid":336070,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T04:28:42.000Z","msg":"快啲落去陪你bb啦鋮俊哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a32a17378988b0f395eb15dab02137be7f44fb22","tid":2330424,"uid":335434,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T04:42:50.000Z","msg":"鋮浚哥會唔會喺屋企病發暴斃都無人知架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69624e40a40054cc1e90632f1a301960ac6fb84e","tid":2330424,"uid":7323,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-